---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Intelligence | Levenhall" description="Levenhall Intelligence is a real-time defense and geopolitical operating picture — 119 feeds, on-device ML, and a proprietary Country Instability Index, fused into one WebGL globe.">

    <!-- ── HERO ── -->
    <section class="intel-hero">
        <div class="hero-bg"></div>
        <div class="hero-grid-overlay"></div>
        <div class="hero-scanlines"></div>

        <span class="hud-bracket hud-tl"></span>
        <span class="hud-bracket hud-tr"></span>
        <span class="hud-bracket hud-bl"></span>
        <span class="hud-bracket hud-br"></span>

        <div class="hero-inner">
            <div class="intel-badge">A Levenhall Product</div>
            <p class="intel-eyebrow">Levenhall</p>
            <h1 class="intel-wordmark">INTELLIGENCE</h1>
            <p class="intel-sub">A Live Operating Picture for Defense &amp; Geopolitics</p>
            <div class="hero-rule"></div>
            <p class="hero-description">Every signal that matters &mdash; conflict, unrest, economy, infrastructure, climate &mdash; on one WebGL globe. Powered by on-device machine learning and Levenhall's proprietary instability index.</p>
            <div class="hero-cta">
                <a href="https://intel.levenhall.com" class="btn btn-gold" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open Intelligence</a>
                <a href="#whats-inside" class="btn btn-outline-white">What's Inside</a>
            </div>
            <p class="hero-live">Live at <span class="hero-live-url">intel.levenhall.com</span></p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── AT A GLANCE ── -->
    <section class="section glance-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="glance-grid reveal">
                <div class="glance-card">
                    <span class="glance-value">119</span>
                    <span class="glance-label">Intelligence Feeds</span>
                </div>
                <div class="glance-card">
                    <span class="glance-value">34</span>
                    <span class="glance-label">Map Layers</span>
                </div>
                <div class="glance-card">
                    <span class="glance-value">27</span>
                    <span class="glance-label">Dashboard Panels</span>
                </div>
                <div class="glance-card">
                    <span class="glance-value">31</span>
                    <span class="glance-label">Tier-1 Countries</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── THE PITCH ── -->
    <section class="section pitch-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="pitch-text reveal">
                <span class="section-label">The Idea</span>
                <h2>One screen. Every signal. <span class="muted">Nothing leaves your browser.</span></h2>
                <div class="gold-rule"></div>
                <p>The heavy machine learning &mdash; embeddings, sentiment, summarization, named-entity extraction &mdash; runs in the analyst's own browser. No round-trip. No leakage.</p>
                <p>The result is a defense-grade dashboard that loads anywhere there's a tab, scales with the analyst rather than the back end, and shows Levenhall's analytical stack at work.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── WHAT'S INSIDE (DARK) ── -->
    <section class="section inside-section" id="whats-inside">
        <div class="inside-bg"></div>
        <div class="container" style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
            <div class="section-header reveal">
                <span class="dark-label">What's Inside</span>
                <h2>Six Modules. One Data Spine.</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="modules-grid reveal">
                <div class="module-card">
                    <span class="module-num">01</span>
                    <h3>Country Instability Index</h3>
                    <p>A proprietary 0&ndash;100 composite tracking instability across 31 Tier-1 countries. Conflict, unrest, information, and security &mdash; weighted, modified, and tiered <strong>Low &rarr; Critical</strong>.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="module-card">
                    <span class="module-num">02</span>
                    <h3>Geo-Convergence</h3>
                    <p>The globe split into 1&deg; cells. When conflict, protest, military, and news signals cluster in the same cell in 24 hours, the system flags an emerging hotspot &mdash; before mainstream reporting does.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="module-card">
                    <span class="module-num">03</span>
                    <h3>Strategic Risk</h3>
                    <p>One number per region, blending convergence (30%), country instability (50%), and infrastructure cascade risk (20%).</p>
                </div>
                <div class="module-card">
                    <span class="module-num">04</span>
                    <h3>Signal Bridge</h3>
                    <p>A unified bus ingesting conflict, unrest, economy, cyber, military, and climate streams. Routes prioritized signals across modules and into the wider Levenhall stack.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="module-card">
                    <span class="module-num">05</span>
                    <h3>On-Device ML</h3>
                    <p>Four ONNX models running in a Web Worker. Embeddings (MiniLM), sentiment (DistilBERT), summarization (FLAN-T5), and NER (BERT). 200 MB budget. Zero server roundtrips.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="module-card">
                    <span class="module-num">06</span>
                    <h3>Cascade Analysis</h3>
                    <p>Models the dependencies between undersea cables, power grids, pipelines, and data centers &mdash; so a disruption in one tells you what falls next.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── THE MAP ── -->
    <section class="section map-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="map-grid reveal">
                <div class="map-text">
                    <span class="section-label">The Map</span>
                    <h2>A WebGL Globe with 34 Layers</h2>
                    <div class="gold-rule"></div>
                    <p>DeckGL + MapLibre. Defense-HUD aesthetic. Eleven layers on by default; the rest a click away.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="map-callout">
                    <div class="map-callout-row">
                        <span class="map-callout-num">11</span>
                        <span class="map-callout-label">On by default</span>
                        <p>Conflicts, military bases &amp; assets, sanctions, hotspots, nuclear facilities, waterways, infrastructure outages, natural disasters, economic indicators, weather.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="map-callout-row">
                        <span class="map-callout-num">23</span>
                        <span class="map-callout-label">A click away</span>
                        <p>Undersea cables, pipelines, AIS, cyber threats, data centers, protests, military flights, spaceports, critical minerals, satellite fires, displacement camps, climate anomalies, financial centers, and more.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── COVERAGE (LIGHT) ── -->
    <section class="section coverage-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header reveal">
                <span class="section-label">Tier-1 Coverage</span>
                <h2>31 Nations at the Core of Allied Posture</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="coverage-grid reveal">
                <div class="coverage-card">
                    <span class="cov-cat cov-cat-allied">NATO &amp; Allied</span>
                    <span class="cov-count">6</span>
                    <span class="cov-flags-row">🇺🇸 🇬🇧 🇫🇷 🇩🇪 🇵🇱 🇦🇺</span>
                </div>
                <div class="coverage-card">
                    <span class="cov-cat cov-cat-adversary">Adversarial</span>
                    <span class="cov-count">4</span>
                    <span class="cov-flags-row">🇷🇺 🇨🇳 🇮🇷 🇰🇵</span>
                </div>
                <div class="coverage-card">
                    <span class="cov-cat cov-cat-conflict">Active Conflict</span>
                    <span class="cov-count">13</span>
                    <span class="cov-flags-row">🇺🇦 🇸🇾 🇾🇪 🇲🇲 🇸🇩 🇪🇹 🇨🇩 🇸🇴 🇦🇫 🇮🇶 🇱🇾 🇳🇬 🇱🇧</span>
                </div>
                <div class="coverage-card">
                    <span class="cov-cat cov-cat-regional">Strategic Powers</span>
                    <span class="cov-count">8</span>
                    <span class="cov-flags-row">🇮🇳 🇵🇰 🇸🇦 🇹🇷 🇦🇪 🇧🇷 🇻🇪 🇹🇼</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── SIBLING PRODUCTS ── -->
    <section class="section siblings-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="siblings-grid reveal">
                <div class="siblings-text">
                    <span class="section-label">Where It Sits</span>
                    <h2>One of Three Levenhall Products</h2>
                    <div class="gold-rule"></div>
                    <p>Intelligence is the live, public-facing dashboard. <strong>BRIDGER</strong> is the federal contracting platform. <strong>AIGIS</strong> is the AI evaluation infrastructure.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="siblings-cards">
                    <a href="/products/bridger" class="sibling-card">
                        <h4>BRIDGER</h4>
                        <p>Market entry intelligence for US federal contracting.</p>
                        <span class="sibling-arrow">&rarr;</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/products/aigis" class="sibling-card">
                        <h4>AIGIS</h4>
                        <p>AI evaluation &amp; governance, unclassified through TS/SCI.</p>
                        <span class="sibling-arrow">&rarr;</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── CTA ── -->
    <section class="intel-cta">
        <div class="intel-cta-bg"></div>
        <div class="intel-cta-inner">
            <div class="intel-cta-accent"></div>
            <div class="intel-cta-badge">Live Now</div>
            <h2>Open the dashboard.</h2>
            <p>A verified email unlocks the full operating picture. Bespoke deployments are available through Levenhall's intelligence practice.</p>
            <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center;">
                <a href="https://intel.levenhall.com" class="btn btn-gold" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open Intelligence</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline-white">Contact Levenhall</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
    /* ── HERO ── */
    .intel-hero {
        background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, #0c2540 0%, #060c18 70%, #03060d 100%);
        padding: 10rem 2rem 6rem;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        min-height: 80vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-bg {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
            radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 40%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.08) 0%, transparent 55%),
            radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 80%, rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.18) 0%, transparent 50%);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-grid-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
            linear-gradient(rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 80px 80px;
        pointer-events: none;
        mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 25%, transparent 75%);
        -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 25%, transparent 75%);
    }

    .hero-scanlines {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 50%, transparent 50%);
        background-size: 100% 3px;
        pointer-events: none;
        mix-blend-mode: overlay;
        opacity: 0.4;
    }

    .hud-bracket {
        position: absolute;
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        border: 2px solid var(--gold);
        opacity: 0.55;
    }
    .hud-tl { top: 24px; left: 24px; border-right: none; border-bottom: none; }
    .hud-tr { top: 24px; right: 24px; border-left: none; border-bottom: none; }
    .hud-bl { bottom: 24px; left: 24px; border-right: none; border-top: none; }
    .hud-br { bottom: 24px; right: 24px; border-left: none; border-top: none; }

    .intel-hero::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, var(--gold) 50%, transparent 100%);
        opacity: 0.55;
    }

    .hero-inner {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .intel-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.68rem;
        letter-spacing: 3.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        background: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.18);
        padding: 0.5rem 1.4rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }

    .intel-eyebrow {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 6px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
        margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
        text-indent: 6px;
    }

    .intel-wordmark {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 10px;
        color: #fff;
        line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        text-indent: 10px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 30%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.7) 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .intel-sub {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.85);
        margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }

    .hero-rule {
        width: 60px;
        height: 2px;
        background: var(--gold);
        margin: 0 auto 1.8rem;
    }

    .hero-description {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
        line-height: 1.8;
        max-width: 580px;
        margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    }

    .hero-cta {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
    }

    .hero-live {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    }

    .hero-live-url {
        color: var(--gold);
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: none;
    }

    /* ── SHARED ── */
    .section-label {
        display: inline-block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.68rem;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--burgundy);
        background: var(--burgundy-surface);
        padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .dark-label {
        display: inline-block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        background: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.15);
        padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .gold-rule {
        width: 50px;
        height: 2px;
        background: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .section-header {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    }

    .section-header h2 { margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
    .section-header p { font-size: 1.02rem; line-height: 1.75; }

    .muted {
        color: var(--text-medium);
        font-weight: 400;
    }

    /* ── AT A GLANCE ── */
    .glance-section {
        background: var(--cream);
        padding: 3.5rem 0;
    }

    .glance-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        gap: 0;
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #fff;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
        border-top: 3px solid var(--gold);
    }

    .glance-card {
        padding: 2rem 1.4rem;
        text-align: center;
        border-right: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
        transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .glance-card:last-child {
        border-right: none;
    }

    .glance-card:hover {
        background: var(--cream);
    }

    .glance-value {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        font-size: 2.4rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }

    .glance-label {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 1.4px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        line-height: 1.45;
    }

    /* ── PITCH ── */
    .pitch-section {
        background: var(--stone);
        padding: 5rem 0;
    }

    .pitch-text {
        max-width: 760px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .pitch-text h2 {
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .pitch-text .gold-rule {
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .pitch-text p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    /* ── WHAT'S INSIDE (DARK) ── */
    .inside-section {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a1628 0%, var(--navy) 50%, #162d4f 100%);
        padding: 5.5rem 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .inside-bg {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 80%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.04) 0%, transparent 50%);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .inside-section::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
        opacity: 0.4;
    }

    .inside-section h2 { color: #fff; }
    .inside-section .section-header p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55); }

    .modules-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        grid-auto-rows: 1fr;
        gap: 1.2rem;
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .module-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        border-top: 2px solid var(--gold);
        padding: 1.8rem 1.6rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.4rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .module-card:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    }

    .module-num {
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--gold);
        opacity: 0.5;
        line-height: 1;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    }

    .module-card h3 {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    }

    .module-card p {
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    }

    .module-card strong {
        color: var(--gold);
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ── THE MAP ── */
    .map-section {
        background: var(--cream);
        padding: 5rem 0;
    }

    .map-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .map-text h2 {
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .map-text p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--text-medium);
    }

    .map-callout {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.2rem;
    }

    .map-callout-row {
        background: #fff;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
        border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
        padding: 1.4rem 1.6rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
        gap: 0.4rem 1.4rem;
        align-items: start;
    }

    .map-callout-num {
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--gold);
        line-height: 1;
        grid-row: span 2;
    }

    .map-callout-label {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        align-self: end;
    }

    .map-callout-row p {
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        line-height: 1.65;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin: 0;
    }

    /* ── COVERAGE ── */
    .coverage-section {
        background: var(--stone);
        padding: 5rem 0;
    }

    .coverage-section h2 { color: var(--deep-navy); }

    .coverage-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        grid-auto-rows: 1fr;
        gap: 1rem;
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .coverage-card {
        background: #fff;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
        border-top: 3px solid var(--gold);
        padding: 1.6rem 1.4rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.9rem;
        text-align: center;
        align-items: center;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .coverage-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-warm-md);
    }

    .cov-cat {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.62rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        padding: 0.35rem 0.7rem;
    }

    .cov-cat-allied { color: var(--gold); background: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.25); }
    .cov-cat-adversary { color: var(--burgundy); background: var(--burgundy-surface); }
    .cov-cat-conflict { color: #a13e0a; background: rgba(161, 62, 10, 0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(161, 62, 10, 0.18); }
    .cov-cat-regional { color: var(--deep-navy); background: rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.15); }

    .cov-count {
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .cov-flags-row {
